OL,3,CCalls for adequate compensation for
OL,4,Cveterans who suffered under 'gay ban'
OL,6,FCharities have called for LGBT
OL,7,Fveterans who suffered historical
OL,8,Fmistreatment in the armed forces to
OL,9,Freceive adequate compensation, in an
OL,10,Fopen letter to the Prime Minister.
OL,12,FThis comes after veterans minister Al
OL,13,FCarns vowed that a financial redress
OL,14,Fscheme for those who suffered under
OL,15,Fthe "gay ban" would be launched at the
OL,16,Fstart of next year.
