OL,6,FThe letter published on Wednesday
OL,7,Fargues that the cap on compensation
OL,8,Fcould lead to "inadequate and
OL,9,Funacceptably low" payments, with
OL,10,Fsuggestions the average payout would
OL,11,Fbe #12,500.
OL,13,FSignatories of the open letter
OL,14,Faddressed to Sir Keir Starmer include
OL,15,Fthe chief executives of Fighting with
OL,16,FPride, Help for Heroes, the Royal
OL,17,FBritish Legion, Stonewall and Age UK.
