OL,6,FFighting with Pride's campaign
OL,7,Fdirector and Royal Navy veteran Craig
OL,8,FJones said: "The funding intended for
OL,9,Fthis scheme is inadequate and fails to
OL,10,Ftake account of the shocking treatment
OL,11,Finflicted upon a community of veterans
OL,12,Fwho defended our peace and freedom but
OL,13,Fwere treated in a way which the Prime
OL,14,FMinister said had brought dishonour on
OL,15,Four nation.
OL,17,F"This is the moment for the Government
OL,18,Fto do the right thing.
