OL,6,F"We are aware that veterans minister
OL,7,FAl Carns is working hard to find
OL,8,Fgreater funding for this scheme, but
OL,9,Fmore must be done to achieve payments
OL,10,Fthat bring a sense of justice for LGBT
OL,11,FVeterans affected by this awful policy.
OL,13,F"We must not miss the opportunity to
OL,14,Fextend the modern values of the armed
OL,15,Fforces to veterans who were shamed for
OL,16,Fdecades."
