OL,6,FEarlier this month, Mr Carns told the
OL,7,FCommons that the treatment of LGBT
OL,8,Fveterans was "completely and utterly
OL,9,Funacceptable", adding the Government
OL,10,F"will meet the financial redress
OL,11,Fscheme by the end of this year with
OL,12,Fthe launch in January next year".
OL,14,FThe National Audit Office reported
OL,15,Fthat up to 4,000 veterans are expected
OL,16,Fto be eligible for compensation.
