OL,6,FChief executive of Help for Heroes
OL,7,FJames Needham, said: "LGBT+ veterans,
OL,8,Fboth before and immediately after the
OL,9,Flifting of the ban in 2000,
OL,10,Fexperienced an almost unique set of
OL,11,Finjuries due to this discriminatory
OL,12,Fpolicy, including wrongful
OL,13,Fimprisonment, loss of careers and
OL,14,Fpensions and exclusion from the
OL,15,Fveteran community.
OL,26,@oD@VOU
