OL,6,F"While progress has been made since
OL,7,Fthen, we are concerned by the proposed
OL,8,Fcompensation. Based on the
OL,9,FGovernment's estimates, veterans
OL,10,Faffected by the ban would receive an
OL,11,Faverage payment of just #12,500, which
OL,12,Fisn't enough to make up for the damage
OL,13,Fdone to their lives.
OL,15,F"We're also disappointed that a
OL,16,Fpromised debate in Parliament may not
OL,17,Fhappen before the compensation scheme
OL,18,Fstarts, which would be a missed
OL,19,Fopportunity for MPs to discuss and
OL,20,Fensure fairness for those impacted."
